N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 1 ยง 191.2 - Sales; misrepresentation

State Regulations

No person shall sell or offer for sale, or advertise for
sale, eggs for human consumption if the package containing them or the label on
them, or any advertising accompany them, shall bear any statement or device
regarding the eggs which may be false or misleading in any
particular. Notes
